##Job Displacement and Automation##
-How AI is changing jobs

##What is happening?##

-AI can replace some human work
-Many jobs may be affected worldwide
-Around 300 million jobs could be impacted by AI (Goldman Sachs)
-AI could do 30% of current work by 2030 (McKinsey)

##Impact on Workers##
-Some people may lose jobs
-Others may face income insecurity
-Some industries will change more than others
-Some jobs may grow

##Conclusion##

-AI will change jobs
-Some jobs will disappear
-New jobs will be created

